        {
            "title": "上善黃金控股股東本周二減持8.09%股權 持股降至57.19%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上善黃金(01939)公布，控股股東兼主席黃仕坤於本周二(12月2日)減持4140.8萬股，相等於股本的8.09%，令持股降至57.19%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15479673-%e4%b8%8a%e5%96%84%e9%bb%83%e9%87%91%e6%8e%a7%e8%82%a1%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%a8%e4%ba%8c%e6%b8%9b%e6%8c%818-09%e8%82%a1%e6%ac%8a-%e6%8c%81%e8%82%a1%e9%99%8d%e8%87%b357-19",
